                "questionText": "Cho biểu thức <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/4e8ab1d0-0e3a-4403-82e6-b4f3022a1907.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/de2088b6-e832-4bc1-8a3c-abde7f628b4c.png\"/> với <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/203d289a-e0f9-41a6-aed5-69bf6df17b50.png\"/>\n<br>1) Tính giá trị của biểu thức <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/7965b262-dab5-4e26-b0d5-9dffcd1a9730.png\"/> khi <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/742e4f69-c682-4776-8b32-dabfb8d70e6c.png\"/>\n<br>2) Rút gọn biểu thức <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/3dd40b33-f310-41ec-a222-8bc85c3989cc.png\"/>\n<br>3) Tìm tất cả các giá trị không âm của <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/9929fa98-c942-474d-af3d-6fbc8cfa1e2e.png\"/> để biểu thức <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/02ca686e-a3e7-4a73-b5a3-9a832d05a6e9.png\"/> đạt giá trị nguyên. \n",
                "answer": "1) Thay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/da98c0a5-9fc2-4c29-a45e-8bbbd2a4d370.png\"/> vào biểu thức <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/68e03e7e-f408-44b7-9cfb-7f228bf8116d.png\"/> ta được: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/0be238ad-ca85-4bba-9930-3aa147276c52.png\"/>\n<br>2) <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/85eb6dc6-87d5-4d79-88e3-3e745a727e8c.png\"/> với <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/687361a9-61b4-40ce-b347-34c60ac96a45.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/99b23400-66b3-4fa4-8065-b114bb8fc213.png\"/><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/ebcd5b3b-8ee6-4e73-bc89-1d97d38fdc2b.png\"/><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/e8394d68-6fe4-4be0-9daf-b6c792c131d4.png\"/><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/648ae695-f760-4358-996a-d569c4753dbc.png\"/><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/3e6da5fd-f723-485c-a4ad-70b5319649a5.png\"/><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/6cd66f37-180b-42d7-ab02-88ee90d38e22.png\"/>\n<br>Khi đó: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/2d70f480-0ec4-4383-b807-8ce6ac9cd894.png\"/><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/d9d05353-e728-49ba-933a-758873bddc6b.png\"/><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/b3961516-29f5-41be-a821-7e87e9522864.png\"/><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/ef904a3d-b707-4828-ac25-85b408cb5280.png\"/>\n<br>Để <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/3b2d3480-9924-4fce-a165-69b289a19765.png\"/> nguyên thì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/7a07b18a-c936-46ac-9ef3-c3c447230937.png\"/> Ư <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/4679ce94-2e40-4927-99e7-ac86f8cde1f1.png\"/>\n<br>Ta có bảng:<br><img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2025/10/af1fded2-c383-4bba-9dfb-2bde75735e32.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>Do <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/50b28289-1d8d-4a5d-a6b7-f2c332a9d8f9.png\"/> không âm nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/c784e7bf-478d-4c87-b923-6fc611f84a59.png\"/>\n<br>Vậy <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/d0ad46f1-9f33-44c5-801b-e5e665265551.png\"/> là các giá trị cần tìm.\n",
