                "questionText": "1) Tìm tất cả các giá trị của <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/c18c63ed-cc76-436a-b1c9-a679130d056a.png\"/> biết <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/ed8a4c8d-2ff3-4a50-b577-e917b3f4bf88.png\"/>\n<br>2) Cho đa thức <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/bbfe83c4-a03d-4ce3-9a3b-aa809754a7d7.png\"/> có nghiệm <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/363b50a1-9dd3-43e0-9b1f-611d617b3277.png\"/> với a, b là các số hữu tỉ. Chứng minh rằng <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/9493d547-3dac-4e35-a5ff-56496a86f3fa.png\"/> chia hết cho đa thức <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/0e7106ee-2ff4-4dce-8aa3-4fe2838cb841.png\"/>\n",
                "answer": "1) <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/b0c8d20c-3a3f-49ce-8a53-bb74453ec520.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/65d87dca-46c5-4185-ab15-066fb58f8beb.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/9d4511cc-50d1-44f9-bb01-f0e1d80ce950.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/1995994c-be45-4190-8b57-42f61b63e861.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/af494fe8-4b2f-47b3-8157-b4b80659ccdf.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/142ce24d-4631-48a1-aa1d-28b4362f7d24.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/de055d3c-d8d7-4cf6-a0ed-2f514fbfc31d.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/d3435ce1-72da-4692-beda-ae9a92b72ac3.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/d91f8d04-00bd-4baf-a9ba-678e4e48e9b2.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/22910bdf-60ba-47f8-aaed-0aeee8ff7d5a.png\"/>\n<br>Trường hợp 1: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/a8506a64-649d-4960-8bd5-bae24b7131b6.png\"/>\n<br>Trường hợp 2: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/a91063db-54a0-4098-8837-3e0d2b284207.png\"/> thì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/3edeee0d-68f4-4bd8-97b3-5904858968fb.png\"/>\n<br>Trường hợp 3: <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/57e62f3e-8343-4654-a9e9-69aa9461b823.png\"/> thì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/0d10a222-70af-4226-bf9a-50271c5df885.png\"/>\n<br>Vậy <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/33d1a444-1849-4deb-9920-6678ece1239c.png\"/>\n<br>2) Vì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/3cb32a78-7646-4525-95d1-904db8d3a602.png\"/> là nghiệm cùa <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/2b6973f2-0530-4492-96f0-4cc8ba0d47ca.png\"/> nên <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/924e7b99-d812-4553-b16c-e45e0f75194e.png\"/>\n<br>Khi đó <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/48dd7da6-cd3a-4bab-a206-3aa3f0f6c820.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/fd737cf2-85ab-4583-92f5-27a8b304cc95.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/193d230c-7d17-477b-af6d-493a8b26848a.png\"/>\n<br><img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/e36f60ff-8f95-4ff6-9778-00eea140f85f.png\"/>\n<br>Nếu <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/fa9711d6-1f90-4897-a854-6b7ecde49103.png\"/> thì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/d76fdf1c-6b27-4f6c-886e-b83f0a1bcfcf.png\"/> (vô lý)\n<br>Nếu <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/aaae4d90-e989-4d15-9754-8fd8da2b4386.png\"/> thì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/9fb33cc3-1e11-4800-aef4-4c89eb0f1eb0.png\"/> hay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/2168e0d0-e258-4fef-838a-144f89170acd.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/c58c0012-feea-4d34-abde-3f8a2841edca.png\"/>\n<br>Khi đó <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/d907b979-0be6-4894-a733-3f8e77a16582.png\"/>\n<br>Hay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/b231ab9f-4368-4475-8611-9b8b6cc64a62.png\"/> chia hết cho đa thức <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2025/10/33d705a6-8af7-497a-991a-c1b9c0a18bc1.png\"/>\n",
